sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App
    participant Gateway
    participant AuthService
    participant Database
    participant EmailService
    participant Telnyx
    
    User->>App: Enter registration info
    App->>App: Validate input
    App->>Gateway: POST /auth/register
    Gateway->>AuthService: Register user
    
    AuthService->>Database: Check if user exists
    Database-->>AuthService: User not found
    
    AuthService->>AuthService: Hash password
    AuthService->>Database: Create user record
    Database-->>AuthService: User created
    
    AuthService->>Telnyx: Provision phone number
    Telnyx-->>AuthService: Number provisioned
    
    AuthService->>EmailService: Send verification email
    EmailService-->>User: Verification email
    
    AuthService->>Gateway: Return tokens
    Gateway->>App: Registration success
    App->>App: Store tokens securely
    App->>User: Navigate to home


